VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT authorized_networks\s*\{[^}]*value\s*=\s*"0\.0\.0\.0/0"
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:ipv4_enabled\s*=\s*true|authorized_networks && MISSING:require_ssl\s*=\s*true|ssl_mode\s*=\s*"ENCRYPTED_ONLY"|private_network
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects Cloud SQL instances authorized to accept connections from all IP addresses.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Cloud SQL Instance Publicly Exposed.
